Timothy M. Russi 
Executive Compensation
As President Auto Finance at ALLY FINANCIAL INC, Timothy M. Russi  made $3,025,266 in total compensation.  Of this total $541,800 was received as a salary, $1,025,000 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $1,359,636 was awarded as stock and $98,830 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


